added.title: Eggsellent Adventure
added.description: Thomas and Percy have a difficult delivery - getting eggs and other cake ingredients safely to Vicarstown for their bake-off.
added.originalseriesname: Thomas and Friends: All Engines Go

added.title: Calliope Crack-Up
added.description: When the engines are delivering attractions to the annual Harwick Beach Carnival, a series of mistakes causes the precious Calliope to break. Luckily, the engines come up with a creative solution.
added.originalseriesname: Thomas and Friends: All Engines Go

added.title: Snowflakes/Caillou Shoots! He Scores!/Caillou goes Tobogganing
added.description: Caillou eagerly awaits the first snowfall of winter, and imagines himself building the biggest snowman./Caillou wants to play hockey with Billy and the other big kids./Mommy can't find Caillou's toboggan for the playschool tobogganing trip.

added.title: Caillou Plays the Drums/Caillou's Marching Band/Caillou Sings
added.description: Clementine's big brother Billy has a new drum set and is having lots of fun playing as loud as he can./Caillou and his friends are very excited when a real marching band goes by the playschool./The playschool is having a talent show and Caillou wants to sing a song.

added.title: Show and Tell/Caillou the Magician/Caillou's Castle
added.description: Caillou has to decide on a nice surprise to bring to playschool for Show and Tell./Grandma shows Caillou a simple magic trick, which makes him decide to be a magician./Caillou wants to play castles and dragons, even though Gilbert isn't very keen on playing the dragon.

added.title: Caillou of the Antarctic/Deep Sea Caillou/Caillou in the Bayou
added.description: Caillou is playing with Jeffrey and Jason when he gets accidentally pushed down./There's a new girl named Lee Wun in playschool, but she's so shy she won't talk to anybody./The whole family is on the way to the beach but accidentally ends up on a trail through a swamp.

added.title: Magnet Madness/Caillou the Dinosaur Hunter/Caillou the Astronaut
added.description: Caillou is playing with the fridge magnets and learns lots of things about them./The whole family goes on a trip to the natural history museum to look at the dinosaurs./Caillou wants to play with both his friends Clementine and Xavier at the playschool playground.

added.title: Mr Big Duck
added.description: Pato is enjoying playing at being very grown up and doesn't want to join in the games with his friends. Eventually though, Pato and the others realize that playing with friends is much more fun than hanging around being 'cool'.

added.title: Guess What?
added.description: Pocoyo plays a game with us. He shows us a series of different extremely strange shapes and wants us to guess what they are. A fun guessing game, learning to look at things in different ways...

added.title: All for One
added.description: Pocoyo wants to play but Baby Bird is flying up in the sky, Pato and Octopus are helicoptering, Elly is jumping up into outer space and even little Caterpillar transforms into a butterfly and flutters away. Pocoyo feels left out so they get together to help him fly up in the sky along with them.

added.title: Band of Friends
added.description: Pocoyo meets a funny little red shape. At first it teases and hides from him, making him jump and chasing him around. But then it brings along its friends and together they put on a music and dancing show for Pocoyo and his gang.

added.title: Upside Down
added.description: Pato gets stuck hanging upside down from the sky. Pocoyo and the friends try to help him down.

added.title: Sleepover
added.description: Bing & Coco are having a sleepover today! They mix up their bedtimes and Bing shows Coco his nightlight Owly. But what will happen when Coco turns all the lights out to show Bing what Amber, one of her Rainbow Fairy Mice, can do?

added.title: Surprise Machine
added.description: Bing and Sula are in Padget's Shop today when they discover the new surprise machine. But what will happen when Bing's surprise toy isn't the one he was hoping for?

added.title: Dizzy
added.description: Bing wants to do spinning on the spinny chair so Pando pushes him superfast. But what will happen when Bing starts to feel too dizzy and wants to stop?

added.title: House
added.description: Bing is playing "Big Bad Wolf" today with Sula, Coco and Charlie and Bing gets to be the wolf! But what will happen when Bing wants to come into the brick house with everyone else?

added.title: Ice Lolly
added.description: It's hot today so Bing and Flop are having yummy delicious ice pops from Gilly. But what will happen to their ice pops when Bing and Flop are rescuing Froggy from the swimming pool in the garden?

added.title: Boo
added.description: Lucas loves to give his friends a scare on Halloween.

added.title: Never Boop a Robot
added.description: When Lucas boops a robot, he and his friends are chased around House!

added.title: The Breathtaking Bolly Show
added.description: If Mush-Mush had Bolly's speed, he'd want everyone to see just how awesomely fast he was. But Bolly is different - he just likes to use his speed helping Mushables. So when Mush-Mush organizes a big stunt for Bolly, he refuses. He just doesn't like to show off. But Mush-Mush promised everyone a show so a show he will give them with Mush-Mush performing instead of Bolly! Gulp!

added.title: Monsterplant
added.description: Bluster creates a mad scientist's monster from a clump of moss and sends it to scare the Whiffles away. The kindhearted Monsterplant just wants to be friends with them, but the Whiffles are frightened away by how he looks. Share and Dibble work together to show the Whiffles how nice Monsterplant is on the inside.

added.title: Neon Beach Party
added.description: Bluster and his Bad Crowd arrive at a lakeside beach for his summer vacation, unaware that the Care Bears are having their vacation on the opposite shore. Trapped inside Bluster's climate-control dome and forced to spend their vacations together, the Bears must find a way to make friends with their ill-tempered neighbors.

added.title: Work Like a Charm
added.description: Chep becomes obsessed with learning all about Mushlore - all the funny little traditions and things that Mushables believe in. Morel is the expert in Mushlore so Chep becomes his apprentice. But the more Chep discovers about Mushlore the more he becomes a true believer to the point that it becomes quite dangerous!

added.title: The Harder They Fall
added.description: Bugs is embarrassed to admit he doesn't know how to skate.

added.title: Band Together
added.description: The babies learn about music and improvise their own orchestra.

added.title: War of the Weirds
added.description: Marvin the Martian comes to visit, and the babies learn to accept differences.

added.title: Mr. McStuffles
added.description: Daffy doesn't want to give up his old toy, even after he's outgrown it.

added.title: Business as Unusual
added.description: Bugs and Daffy open competing lemonade stands.

added.title: A Rusty Rescue
added.description: When Thomas throws away Diesel's favorite oil can thinking it's trash, he makes a promise to get it back and learns it's better not to touch things that aren't yours.
added.originalseriesname: Thomas and Friends: All Engines Go

added.title: Cake
added.description: Bing is having a cake party today, and is excited to show Sula the raspberry he decorated the cake with especially for her. But it's hard for Sula to see, so what happens when Bing tilts the cake a little too far?

removed.title: Paint Me a Picture!
removed.description: Pocoyo has decided to paint a portrait. But none of his friends will sit still long enough for him to be able to finish his picture. Pocoyo is sad because he feels like he hasn't managed to do what he set out to do - but looking at his picture with fresh eyes he sees that his picture really does capture the true essence of his friends.

removed.title: Caillou and the Big Slide/Caillou the Sailor/Caillou and the Creepy Crawlies
removed.description: The playschool is going swimming, and it's Caillou's very first time on a water slide./Mommy and Daddy are going out to a party and Caillou is excited to hear that Grandpa is coming to babysit./Rosie doesn't like bugs - she thinks they're icky!

removed.title: Where's Flop?
removed.description: It's lunchtime! Bing's hungry for carrots. But what happens when Flop pops to the shops and Bing stays at home with Amma and Sula?

removed.title: Lunchbox
removed.description: It's lunchtime! Bing shows Pando and Sula his brand new Hoppity Voosh lunchbox! And Pando has the exact same one MATCH! But then they mix their lunchboxes up.

removed.title: Elly's Doll
removed.description: Pocoyo is charged with looking after Elly's favorite doll, but he breaks it. Instead of telling her the truth, he pretends to be the doll. It's only when nature gets the better of Pocoyo that Elly realizes what's going on. She forgives Pocoyo warmly and mends her doll.

removed.title: More
removed.description: It's bath time! Bing's excited to do the bubbles, but how much bubble goo does Bing need?

removed.title: Tree
removed.description: Bing and Pando are being diggers, planting trees in the sandpit. What will happen when Pando ruins Bing's digging?

removed.title: Ghost Camp
removed.description: When Lucas and friends go camping, Avocado tells a scary story. Lucas now thinks there's a ghost in the garden.

removed.title: The Tiger Train
removed.description: When Yong Bao visits Sodor, a jealous Thomas sets out to prove he's the braver train and challenges Yong Bao to a series of bravery challenges, only to have his plan backfire.
removed.originalseriesname: Thomas and Friends: All Engines Go

removed.title: Caillou the Road Builder/Caillou's Building Adventure/A House in the Sky
removed.description: There's been a big storm and the playschool yard is littered with branches./When Daddy and Grandpa help a charity build a new home for a needy family, Caillou comes along./Mommy and Caillou go to visit an old friend of Mom's.

removed.title: Sparkle Magic
removed.description: Sula is the fairy queen and shows Bing her special sparkle magic... will Bing find his own?

removed.title: Return of the Gnomes
removed.description: When Gus and Garth's greedy uncle makes his nephews forget the caring, sharing, and generosity they learned from the Care Bears and convinces them to return to their old selfish ways, the Bears must help them remember their caring hearts.

removed.title: Big Jumping Spider
removed.description: Lucas performs epic jumps all around House. Findley is nervous and wishes Lucas wouldn't jump.

removed.title: What's In the Box?
removed.description: Pocoyo's new box takes on a life of its own when Loula accidentally crawls underneath it. Eventually with the help of his friends, Pocoyo works out what's - or WHO'S - in the box.

removed.title: The Light in the Forest
removed.description: Cheer bonds with a migrating firefly-like creature, called a Sparklewing, who stows aboard the Cloudseeker. The two become good friends, but there's a problem: Sparklewings must finish their migration to bring life-giving nutrients to the fields of the Silver Lining. Cheer's difficult and emotional parting with her new friend is only possible once they both accept that it's for a greater good.

removed.title: Musical Blocks
removed.description: Pocoyo and Pato are having great fun playing with some magical blocks which form towers when music is played. But the fun turns to drama when Pato gets stuck on top of a high tower. How can Pocoyo return his ducky friend back to ground safely?

removed.title: Everyone's Best/Stronger Every Day/No More Training Wheels
removed.description: When Clementine shows up with a swimming ribbon on her chest, Caillou really wants to have one too./When a new, longer set of monkey bars is installed at the park, Caillou is disappointed./With training wheels on his bike, Caillou is having trouble keeping up with Sarah.

removed.title: Caillou Helps Out/Caillou the Firefighter/Caillou to the Rescue
removed.description: Rosie is teething and just can't seem to fall asleep./The Fire chief visits Caillou's playschool to teach the children about fire drills./A mischievous Rosie hides Caillou's cars between the cushions on the sofa.

removed.title: Can-Do Submarine Crew
removed.description: Thomas and Percy think they're great communicators, but when they're tasked with delivering a submarine to Vicarstown, communication becomes a bit more difficult… to say the least!
removed.originalseriesname: Thomas and Friends: All Engines Go

removed.title: Caillou Goes Caroling/A Playschool Party/Caillou's Christmas Eve
removed.description: Caillou goes out caroling for the very first time with Mommy, Daddy, Rosie, Grandpa and Grandma./It's a very special day at playschool as they celebrate the many ways of celebrating the holiday season./It's finally Christmas Eve and Caillou just can't wait for nighttime.

removed.title: Wackily Ever After
removed.description: Pocoyo and his friends are playing dressing up and the narrator decides to tell a story. The traditional fairy tale takes on a decidedly wacky hue as the characters all undercut the conventions with hilarious and surprising results.
